{"tid":925304,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一齊嚟旅行啦！","createTime":"2018-12-02T16:18:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-03T05:55:34.000Z","uid":12421,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1107ef315b85a80849752365bc61fc2ff1d5f89f","tid":925304,"uid":12421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T16:18:23.000Z","msg":"在濃霧之中，有一輛馬車停在一座大宅門前。駕座上有個戴著草帽的年輕人，百無聊賴地聽著門前的一人說話。<br />\n<br />\n大宅門前，一個衣裝齊整、身材挺拔的老年人正在跟面前一個身穿華麗長袍的年輕人交代些甚麼。<br />\n<br />\n你是？<br />\n<br />\nA. 馬車上的草帽年輕人<br />\nB. 身穿華麗長袍的年輕人"},{"pid":"fedbec72bd7de73cce4e4111fe35f8a5ddefdc86","tid":925304,"uid":12421,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T16:18:37.000Z","msg":"A. 馬車上的草帽年輕人"},{"pid":"54d682e70057caa6b3a41568ea6215f80d446807","tid":925304,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T16:19:41.000Z","msg":"keep住兩個選擇用正負評玩得唔得"},{"pid":"3f5ef7f9f37ea05bf0137d4a4a334c026c1a37f7","tid":925304,"uid":12421,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T16:19:50.000Z","msg":"B. 身穿華麗長袍的年輕人<br />\n<br />\n不定期更新 但我若果行開過睇票數後 出文前一定會講聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"584dd03f0a1ecbc566da68e7a70498606bb14cac","tid":925304,"uid":12421,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"54d682e70057caa6b3a41568ea6215f80d446807","tid":925304,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T16:19:41.000Z","msg":"keep住兩個選擇用正負評玩得唔得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T16:22:10.000Z","msg":"唔得 故事設定會有智鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當然盡量同一次選擇唔會有好類似嘅選項<br />\n<br />\n同埋講漏咗 人常在就五分鐘check一次票 根據票數出文"},{"pid":"bc791a328b46ed1ad6af35a8feae1723487cced6","tid":925304,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"584dd03f0a1ecbc566da68e7a70498606bb14cac","tid":925304,"uid":12421,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"54d682e70057caa6b3a41568ea6215f80d446807","tid":925304,"uid":7