成壯遊，望少爺珍而重之。」<br />\n<br />\n你接過信封後，決定：<br />\nA. 上馬車，並使喚馬車上的年輕人向前行。<br />\nB. 上馬車，並使喚馬車上的年輕人回頭。<br />\nC. 步入大宅"},{"pid":"68afaf44b498cf0fa2baad06d77119a859024226","tid":925304,"uid":12421,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T16:50:36.000Z","msg":"A. 上馬車，並使喚馬車上的年輕人向前行。"},{"pid":"cd4b819902d42487188be535068dbfc46ee611bf","tid":925304,"uid":12421,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T16:50:49.000Z","msg":"B. 上馬車，並使喚馬車上的年輕人回頭。"},{"pid":"4f3c2e8911d698f5b5dfbb671ca740e24ec03b9f","tid":925304,"uid":12421,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T16:50:59.000Z","msg":"C. 步入大宅"},{"pid":"b008e216be183cede41af396c652c4861e8a608a","tid":925304,"uid":104017,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T16:51:19.000Z","msg":"C"},{"pid":"6c988912fb24c78a118a30d6e116077e113ebf88","tid":925304,"uid":190714,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T16:54:24.000Z","msg":"C"},{"pid":"0a0565af16958b9d5145bb09156182112838ec3c","tid":925304,"uid":12421,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T17:00:37.000Z","msg":"C. 步入大宅<br />\n<br />\n你將信封放進長袍的其中一個口袋裡，然後一言不發地提步邁向大宅。雖然老人的臉孔看起來十分擔心你，但身子仍向側讓過。<br />\n<br />\n你回到家族大宅，決定：<br />\nA. 去找父親<br />\nB. 去找大哥<br />\nC. 去找二哥<br />\nD. 回到自己的房間"},{"pid":"32b5a6c1a83992a817944cfe2c755b7944907687","tid":925304,"uid":12421,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T17:00:48.000Z","msg":"A. 去找父親"},{"pid":"026558d9fd48c2ad37ed12d37af60893b4a874ac","tid":925304,"uid":12421,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T17:01:00.000Z","msg":"B. 去找大哥"},{"pid":"5ef79f6af77996e84905c10eb5a47ec1c0f27d1a","tid":925304,"uid":12421,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T17:01:10.000Z","msg":"C. 去找二哥"},{"pid":"689201c506ed6e35536744e1e62200fcd56ff70f","tid":925304,"uid":12421,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20